{"title_page": "Kygo discography", "text_new": "{{short description|Discography}}\n{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist = [[Kygo]]\n| Image = Kygo i 2014.jpg\n| Caption = Kygo performing in 2014\n| Studio = 3\n| EP = 1\n| Singles = 24\n| Music videos = 19\n| Option name = Promotional singles\n| Option = 8\n| 2Option name = Remixes\n| 2Option = 13<!--Only include record label release-->\n}}\n\nNorwegian DJ [[Kygo]] has released two [[studio album]]s, one [[extended play]], 24 [[single (music)|single]]s, 8 [[promotional single]]s, 13 [[remix]]es<!--Only include record label release--> and 19 [[music video]]s.\n\n== Studio albums ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of studio albums, with selected chart positions, sales figures and certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:12em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.9em;font-size:90%;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br /><ref name=\"NOR\">{{cite web | url=http://norwegiancharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Kygo | title=Discography Kygo | publisher=Hung Medien | work=norwegiancharts.com | accessdate=18 November 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.9em;font-size:90%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br /><ref name=\"AUS\">Peaks in Australia:\n* All except noted: {{cite web | url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Kygo | title=Discography Kygo | publisher=Hung Medien | work=australian-charts.com | accessdate=24 June 2015}}\n* \"Nothing Left\": {{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-singles-one-direction-drag-me-down-is-no-1-20150808|title=ARIA Singles: One Direction 'Drag Me Down' Is No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=8 August 2015|accessdate=8 August 2015}}\n* \"Stole the Show\": {{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-singles-justin-bieber-what-do-you-mean-spends-second-week-at-no-1-20150912|title=ARIA Singles: Justin Bieber 'What Do You Mean?' Spends Second Week At No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=12 September 2015|accessdate=12 September 2015}}\n* \"Here for You\": {{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/music-news-aria-singles-adele-earns-platinum-status-with-hello-at-no-1-20151107|title=ARIA Singles: Adele Earns Platinum Status with 'Hello' at No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=7 November 2015|accessdate=7 November 2015}}\n* \"Stay\": {{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-singles-flume-never-be-like-you-is-no-1-20160213|title=ARIA Singles: Flume 'Never Be Like You' Is No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=13 February 2016|accessdate=13 February 2016}}\n* \"Fragile\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2016/03/chart-watch-361/|title=CHART WATCH #361|publisher=auspOp|date=26 March 2016|accessdate=26 March 2016}}\n* \"Carry Me\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2016/08/chart-watch-383/|title=CHART WATCH #383|publisher=auspOp|date=27 August 2016|accessdate=27 August 2016}}\n* ''Stargazing'' EP: {{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=20 November 2017|accessdate=18 November 2017}}\n* \"Kids in Love\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2017/10/aria-chart-watch-444/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #444|publisher=auspOp|date=28 October 2017|accessdate=28 October 2017}}\n* \"Not Ok\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2019/6/aria-chart-watch-527/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #526|publisher=auspOp|date=1 June 2019|accessdate=1 June 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.9em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL<br />(FL)]]<br /><ref name=\"BELFL\">{{cite web | url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Kygo | title=Discografie Kygo | publisher=Hung Medien | work=u